concept.definition: Supply has been requested, but not dispensed.
Supply has been received by the requestor.
The supply will not be completed because the supplier was unable or unwilling to supply the item.
The orderer of the supply cancelled the request.

text.div:
SupplyRequestStatus

Status of the supply request

This value set has an inline code system http://hl7.org/fhir/supplyrequest-status, which defines the following codes:

CodeDisplayDefinition
requested RequestedSupply has been requested, but not dispensed.
completed ReceivedSupply has been received by the requestor.
failed FailedThe supply will not be completed because the supplier was unable or unwilling to supply the item.
cancelled CancelledThe orderer of the supply cancelled the request.
